ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR ADVOCACY USE:

This intelligence platform is specifically designed for legitimate advocacy, 
legal reform, journalism, and policy development purposes. Users are encouraged
to:

1. Share this platform with reform organizations and advocacy groups
2. Use the intelligence for educational and awareness purposes
3. Reference data and strategies in policy proposals and legal filings
4. Adapt frameworks for local reform campaigns

The intelligence contained herein is compiled from public sources and is 
intended to support efforts to protect children and reform systemic issues
in the juvenile justice system.